data.title: About: Tomie Unlimited
data.meta_description: Tomie Unlimited (富江　アンリミテッド, Tomie anrimiteddo) is a 2011 Japanese psychological-body horror film directed by Noboru Iguchi and the eighth installment and reboot of the Tomie film series.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

Tomie Unlimited (富江 アンリミテッド, Tomie anrimiteddo) is a 2011 Japanese psychological-body horror film directed by Noboru Iguchi and the eighth installment and reboot of the Tomie film series. (en)

토미에 언리미티드는 이토 준지에 원작을 영화화한 공포 영화이다. 토미에 언리미티드는 최신 시리즈이다. (ko)
